## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **lenacapavir Sunlenca 2022 → PrEP 2024-25 6-monthly subcutaneous** = first-in-class capsid inhibitor (HIV-1 CA hexamer interface). PURPOSE-1 (cisgender women sub-Saharan) → 99% effective + 0 infection in ITT. groundbreaking — 6-month → 12-month research path = quantum-VQE 의 capsid pocket variant binding 직접 fit. hxq-prev-lena-001 candidate.
2. **cabotegravir-LA Apretude 2021** = first long-acting injectable PrEP (HPTN 083/084). 2-monthly IM. integrase strand-transfer inhibitor. lenacapavir 와 mechanism 다른 path.
3. **nirsevimab Beyfortus 2023 FDA** = first universal infant RSV mAb prophylaxis (palivizumab high-risk only → universal <8mo). 4× longer half-life (YTE Fc mod) — single-dose season-long. 2023-24 시즌 first roll-out + 공급 부족. clesrovimab CTGEN-201 (Merck) + 후속 next-gen.
4. **abrysvo + arexvy + mResvia RSV vaccine 2023** = first RSV vaccine 60-year wait. preF (DS-Cav1 stabilization breakthrough — McLellan 2013). abrysvo 임신부 32-36주 → transplacental Ab → 영아 보호. 60+ 1회 1조 수십억 시장.
5. **HPV vaccine 9-valent Gardasil 9 (2014 → 2023 9-26 expanded → 2024 27-45 expanded)** = primary cervical cancer prevention 90%+ HPV strain coverage. WHO 2030 cervical cancer elimination 목표 핵심. quantum-VQE 의 L1 pentamer + neutralizing Ab binding fit.
6. **low-dose aspirin USPSTF 2022 reversal** = 60+ 비권고 (출혈 위험 vs CV benefit 균형 무너짐). 40-59 individualized (10y CV risk ≥10% + low bleeding). ASPREE + ARRIVE + ASCEND 후 evidence shift. CRC chemoprevention separate (long-term).
7. **statin primary prevention USPSTF 2022 update** = 40-75 + 1+ CV risk + 10y ASCVD ≥10% (B grade). 76+ + 10y 6-10% (C grade individualized). 10-year-event 기반 NNT calculator + shared-decision-making.
8. **semaglutide SELECT 2023** = obese non-DM + 기존 CVD → 20% MACE 감소. first GLP-1 primary CV prevention indication (FDA 2024 expansion). 비만 + CVD primary prev path = quantum-VQE 의 GLP-1R + biased agonist fit.
9. **canakinumab CANTOS 2017** = first anti-inflammatory CV prevention (anti-IL-1β). hsCRP-guided. fatal infection 균형 → 임상 채택 제한 + off-label. inflammatory pathway primary prev path 개념입증 의의.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, preventive medicine 임상 현실 한정.

